ANKARA, Turkey, December 20, 2019/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            We are saddened to receive the news that many people lost their lives and injured in a terrorist attack against a fishing village on the shores of Lake Chad.



We strongly condemn this heinous attack. We extend our condolences to the brotherly people and Government of Chad. We wish Allahâ€™s mercy upon those who lost their lives and speedy recovery for those who were injured.